{"tid":1430142,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我！哋！無！大！台！","createTime":"2019-08-07T16:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T03:38:27.000Z","uid":116775,"like":167,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"b0d3afe66c05b6135c2d9c1c30e398420dc6888e","tid":1430142,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:13:06.000Z","msg":"今日開始不斷有人開始帶風向&mdash;要重組大台，更甚者直言沒有大台的運動走不遠。<br />\n<br />\n但我希望再次提醒大家，我哋無大台，唔可能有大台，唔可以有大台。呢個運動之所以比雨革走得更遠，更有成效，究其本質就是沒有領導，全賴群眾智慧。我們再次回望雨革之失敗其因&mdash;大台。因為政府可以將矛頭直指大台，分化群眾，令運動失焦。堡壘往往從內部開始崩塌，只要無大台，政府可以攻擊的地方就少一個，而且每個人的聲音就更容易被聽見！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">為了以正視聽，解除公眾誤解，我想請泛民主派議員和民間記者會再次重申「沒有大台，只有群眾」丶「不分化不割蓆」嘅立場，以免造成紛爭誤會。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"d7c48c8322ea3d8c35a243fe7302ccca4afecd67","tid":1430142,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"1205d38555c5782bcbb888192b3a3185787c9bff","tid":1430142,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:13:59.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"a5dbbb2733591192355d0832349b028a6d13855e","tid":1430142,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"三<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9779d4f922048d13a2ddbbf037c4e0423af47ac3","tid":1430142,"uid":102308,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XjcOpRk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXjcOpRk.jpg&h=4850de5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2VkfX0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2VkfX0.jpg&h=3aceafd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VpnnupT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVpnnupT.png&h=bf703274&s={SIZE}\" />"